ReadMe

Drill ID: JD_2026_06_W4_LibraryBorrowTracker

Class Name: LibraryBorrowTracker

Difficulty: Level 2 — Multi-Class Application

Estimated Time: 45–60 minutes

Actual Time Taken: 48 minutes

Written by: Chanwoo Park

Problem
Create a console-based library borrow tracking program.

Program Flow
LibraryMain creates a Scanner and one LibraryService object. The main method controls
the menu and calls LibraryService methods. LibraryService owns the book list and performs
all book-related operations.

Class Responsibilities
LibraryMain controls the menu only.
Book represents one book.
LibraryService manages the collection of books.

Object Collaboration
LibraryMain calls LibraryService. LibraryService creates and manages Book objects.
LibraryMain must not directly manage ArrayList<Book>.